trans-unit.source: Specifies the localization attributes for a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_baml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-baml-md.md)] class or class member.
trans-unit.target: Angir lokalisering attributtene for en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_baml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-baml-md.md)] klassen eller klassen medlem.

trans-unit.source: This attribute can be applied to a class, property, or method.
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet kan brukes i en klasse, egenskap eller metode.

trans-unit.source: For more information on how to use localization attributes, see [Localization Attributes and Comments](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker lokalisering attributter [lokalisering attributter og kommentarer](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.LocalizabilityAttribute"></xref> class with a specified localization category.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.LocalizabilityAttribute"> </xref> klassen med en angitt lokalisering kategori.

trans-unit.source: Gets the category setting of the localization attribute's targeted value.
trans-unit.target: Henter kategori innstillingen for attributtet lokalisering målverdien.

trans-unit.source: The category setting of the localization attribute.
Gets or sets the modifiability setting of the localization attribute's targeted value.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir modifiability innstillingen for attributtet lokalisering målverdien.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the modifiability settings of the localization attribute.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser modifiability innstillingene for attributtet lokalisering.

trans-unit.source: |Modifiability setting|Meaning| |---------------------------|-------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>|Targeted value is modifiable by localizers.| |<xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>|Targeted value is not modifiable by localizers.| |<xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>|Targeted value's modifiability is inherited from its parent node.|
trans-unit.target: | Modifiability innstillingen | Det vil si | |---------------------------|-------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>| Målverdien kan endres ved localizers. | | <xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>| Målverdien er ikke kan endres ved localizers. | | <xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>| Angitt verdien modifiability er arvet fra den overordnede noden. |</xref:System.Windows.Modifiability> </xref:System.Windows.Modifiability> </xref:System.Windows.Modifiability>

trans-unit.source: The modifiability setting of the localization attribute.
Gets or sets the readability setting of the localization attribute's targeted value.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir lese innstillingen for attributtet lokalisering målverdien.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the readability settings of the localization attribute.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser lese innstillingene for attributtet lokalisering.

trans-unit.source: |Readability setting|Meaning| |-------------------------|-------------| |<xref:System.Windows.Readability>|Targeted value is readable text.| |<xref:System.Windows.Readability>|Targeted value is not readable.| |<xref:System.Windows.Readability>|Targeted value's readability is inherited from its parent node.|
trans-unit.target: | Innstillingen for å lese | Det vil si | |-------------------------|-------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Readability>| Målverdien er lesbar tekst. | | <xref:System.Windows.Readability>| Målverdien er ikke lesbar. | | <xref:System.Windows.Readability>| Lese på angitte verdien er arvet fra den overordnede noden. |</xref:System.Windows.Readability> </xref:System.Windows.Readability> </xref:System.Windows.Readability>
